$ v$log_file

This view can be queried to find the filenames, group numbers and states of → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/redo-log-files[redo log files].
-
Compare with → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/log

For example, to find all files of group 2, use
code {
select
  member
from
  v$logfile
where
  group# = 2
code }

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/[Oracle Dynamic Performance Views]
